Title: Sephora Shine Lipstick 3.9 g(Loveable Cotton Candy Pink - N06)
Description: What it is:A moisturizing lipstick with a rich, glossy shine. What it does:Show-off your gorgeous smile with this easy-to-wear formula that offers heightened transparency and shine. Lips will look brilliant while drenched in this collection of glossy, shimmering, and metallic hues. The Hydra-Comfort complex blend of moisturizing oils and antioxidiant vitamin E ensures optimal comfort, while nourishing and protecting your lips. The glossy shades include clear pigments and carnauba wax for a dazzling, wet-lip look. The shimmering and metallic formulas contain 3D shimmering particles and shea butter for extreme radiance. The precise product design enables a flawless lip definition and the vast array of shades will compliment your entire wardrobe.Suggested Usage:-Apply a very light coat of loose powder on lips before applying lipstick to set color. -For a more intense glossy effect, apply a touch of clear lip gloss over lipstick. (Glossy Gloss #01 Clear or Ultra Shine #01 Totally lucid). -For a perfect lip shape: start in the middle of the lips and smooth out to the corners of the mouth.

Title: L'Oreal Paris Nutrishine by Color Riche(Vivid Rose - 122)
Description: A lipstick that cares like a balm and gives you the glamorous shine of a gloss – wouldn’t that be something! Loreal Paris gives you just that in its range of Nutrishine by Color Riche lip colors. Nourishment of Lip Balm and Shine of Lip Gloss  With a fine blend of indulgent emollients, this Nutrishine lip color in the shade Vivid Rose – 122 pampers your lips to a burst of moisture and also offers a sleek, glossy finish. Contains Royal Jelly  Royal jelly is a precious natural ingredient that instantly melts into your lips and makes it look cushiony soft and dewy. Powered with Shea Butter The creamy formula is also enriched with shea butter and Vitamins A, E and F to make your lips smooth and alluring. Non-sticky Finish So creamy yet non-sticky, this Loreal Paris Lip Color makes your lips look fab and prevents hair getting stuck on your lips. Totally spectacular!

Finally it descends into the base note which holds heavy hints of musk with smoky amber and earthy patchouli. This aromatic fragragrance redolent with woody elements and a generous sprinkling of citrus exudes a sensuous earthy scent that is ideal for a romantic evening.
